ROOT CAUSE: The migration disables foreign key checks only after the table rename completes. When SQLite renames `tasks` to `__new_tasks`, it temporarily drops and recreates the table, which triggers ON DELETE CASCADE on all referencing foreign keys (task_events.task_id) before the rename finishes. The PRAGMA takes effect only after this damage occurs.

